name: Suicide Man
description: Depression. PTSD. ADHD. The perfect combination to an early death. All three of which either go misdiagnosed or untreated and are often found together. Suicide Man represents the smile on the out side which is a front to what they’re feeling on the inside which is that they’re already dead or on their way to be another one of the 130 suicides a day. Look at him and remember that there is a warm heart inside that tin man who wants and needs understanding love and acceptance.
